name: Jaime L. Garcia
text: Re: Warning shot being cut, depends on the cinema.    I actually thought originally na nasa loob ng plastic yun tomatoes, but damn, they're not. Occam's Razor would suggest that the tomatoes be in the plastic bag, but I guess they didn't spill out well enough, so direk asks the girl to just drop them instead.     She's even carrying the tomatoes in two batches (one per hand)!  https://youtu.be/w4pwJvJGNLk?t=2
